#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.describe.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.describe"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:1 of
msgid "Generate descriptive statistics."
msgstr "生成描述性统计信息。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:3 of
msgid ""
"Descriptive statistics include those that summarize the central tendency,"
" dispersion and shape of a dataset's distribution, excluding ``NaN`` "
"values."
msgstr ""
"描述性统计包括总结数据集分布的中心趋势、离散程度和形状的统计量，不包括 ``"
"NaN`` 值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:7 of
msgid ""
"Analyzes both numeric and object series, as well as ``DataFrame`` column "
"sets of mixed data types. The output will vary depending on what is "
"provided. Refer to the notes below for more detail."
msgstr ""
"分析数值型和对象型序列，以及混合数据类型的 ``DataFrame`` 列集合。输出将"
"根据提供的内容而变化。有关更多详细信息，请参阅下面的说明。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:12 of
msgid ""
"The percentiles to include in the output. All should fall between 0 and "
"1. The default is ``[.25, .5, .75]``, which returns the 25th, 50th, and "
"75th percentiles."
msgstr ""
"要包含在输出中的百分位数。所有值都应在 0 和 1 之间。默认值为 ``[.25, .5, "
".75]``，返回第 25、50 和 75 百分位数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:17 of
msgid ""
"A white list of data types to include in the result. Ignored for "
"``Series``. Here are the options:  - 'all' : All columns of the input "
"will be included in the output. - A list-like of dtypes : Limits the "
"results to the   provided data types.   To limit the result to numeric "
"types submit   ``numpy.number``. To limit it instead to object columns "
"submit   the ``numpy.object`` data type. Strings   can also be used in "
"the style of   ``select_dtypes`` (e.g. ``df.describe(include=['O'])``). -"
" None (default) : The result will include all numeric columns."
msgstr ""
"要包含在结果中的数据类型白名单。对 ``Series`` 会忽略。选项如下：  - 'all'"
" : 输入的所有列都将包含在输出中。 - 类列表的 dtypes : 将结果限制为提供的"
"数据类型。   要将结果限制为数值类型，请提交 ``numpy.number``。   要将其"
"限制为对象列，请提交 ``numpy.object`` 数据类型。   字符串也可以使用 ``"
"select_dtypes`` 的风格（例如 ``df.describe(include=['O'])``）。 - None（"
"默认） : 结果将包含所有数值列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:17 of
msgid ""
"A white list of data types to include in the result. Ignored for "
"``Series``. Here are the options:"
msgstr "要包含在结果中的数据类型的白名单。对 ``Series`` 忽略。以下是选项："

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:20 of
msgid "'all' : All columns of the input will be included in the output."
msgstr "'all' : 输入的所有列都将包含在输出中。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:21 of
msgid ""
"A list-like of dtypes : Limits the results to the provided data types. To"
" limit the result to numeric types submit ``numpy.number``. To limit it "
"instead to object columns submit the ``numpy.object`` data type. Strings "
"can also be used in the style of ``select_dtypes`` (e.g. "
"``df.describe(include=['O'])``)."
msgstr ""
"类似列表的 dtypes : 将结果限制为提供的数据类型。要将结果限制为数值类型，"
"请提交 ``numpy.number``。要将其限制为对象列，请提交 ``numpy.object`` "
"数据类型。字符串也可以在 ``select_dtypes`` 风格中使用（例如 ``df.describe"
"(include=['O'])``）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:28 of
msgid "None (default) : The result will include all numeric columns."
msgstr "None（默认）: 结果将包含所有数值列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:30 of
msgid ""
"A black list of data types to omit from the result. Ignored for "
"``Series``. Here are the options:  - A list-like of dtypes : Excludes the"
" provided data types   from the result. To exclude numeric types submit"
"   ``numpy.number``. To exclude object columns submit the data   type "
"``numpy.object``. Strings can also be used in the style of   "
"``select_dtypes`` (e.g. ``df.describe(exclude=['O'])``). - None (default)"
" : The result will exclude nothing."
msgstr ""
"要从结果中排除的数据类型黑名单。对 ``Series`` 会忽略。选项如下：  - 类"
"列表的 dtypes : 从结果中排除提供的数据类型。   要排除数值类型，请提交 ``"
"numpy.number``。   要排除对象列，请提交 ``numpy.object`` 数据类型。   "
"字符串也可以使用 ``select_dtypes`` 的风格（例如 ``df.describe(exclude=['O"
"'])``）。 - None（默认） : 结果将不排出任何内容。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:30 of
msgid ""
"A black list of data types to omit from the result. Ignored for "
"``Series``. Here are the options:"
msgstr "要从结果中省略的数据类型的黑名单。对 ``Series`` 忽略。以下是选项："

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:33 of
msgid ""
"A list-like of dtypes : Excludes the provided data types from the result."
" To exclude numeric types submit ``numpy.number``. To exclude object "
"columns submit the data type ``numpy.object``. Strings can also be used "
"in the style of ``select_dtypes`` (e.g. ``df.describe(exclude=['O'])``)."
msgstr ""
"类似列表的 dtypes : 从结果中排除提供的数据类型。要排除数值类型，请提交 ``"
"numpy.number``。要排除对象列，请提交 ``numpy.object`` 数据类型。字符串也"
"可以在 ``select_dtypes`` 风格中使用（例如 ``df.describe(exclude=['O'])``"
"）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:38 of
msgid "None (default) : The result will exclude nothing."
msgstr "None（默认）: 结果将不排除任何内容。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:41 of
msgid "Summary statistics of the Series or Dataframe provided."
msgstr "提供的 Series 或 Dataframe 的摘要统计信息。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:46 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.count`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:47 of
msgid "Count number of non-NA/null observations."
msgstr "计算非 NA/空值的观测数量。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:49 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.max`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:50 of
msgid "Maximum of the values in the object."
msgstr "对象中值的最大值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:52 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.min`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:53 of
msgid "Minimum of the values in the object."
msgstr "对象中值的最小值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:55 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.mean`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:56 of
msgid "Mean of the values."
msgstr "值的平均值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:58 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.std`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:59 of
msgid "Standard deviation of the observations."
msgstr "观测值的标准差。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:61 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.select_dtypes`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:62 of
msgid "Subset of a DataFrame including/excluding columns based on their dtype."
msgstr "基于 dtype 包含/排除列的 DataFrame 子集。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:65 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:66 of
msgid ""
"For numeric data, the result's index will include ``count``, ``mean``, "
"``std``, ``min``, ``max`` as well as lower, ``50`` and upper percentiles."
" By default the lower percentile is ``25`` and the upper percentile is "
"``75``. The ``50`` percentile is the same as the median."
msgstr ""
"对于数值型数据，结果的索引将包括 ``count``、``mean``、``std``、``min``、`"
"`max`` 以及下分位数、``50`` 分位数和上分位数。默认情况下，下分位数是 ``25"
"``，上分位数是 ``75``。``50`` 分位数即中位数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:72 of
msgid ""
"For object data (e.g. strings or timestamps), the result's index will "
"include ``count``, ``unique``, ``top``, and ``freq``. The ``top`` is the "
"most common value. The ``freq`` is the most common value's frequency. "
"Timestamps also include the ``first`` and ``last`` items."
msgstr ""
"对于对象型数据（例如字符串或时间戳），结果的索引将包括 ``count``、``"
"unique``、``top`` 和 ``freq``。``top`` 是最常见的值。``freq`` 是最常见值"
"的频率。时间戳还包括 ``first`` 和 ``last`` 项。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:77 of
msgid ""
"If multiple object values have the highest count, then the ``count`` and "
"``top`` results will be arbitrarily chosen from among those with the "
"highest count."
msgstr ""
"如果有多个对象值具有相同的最高计数，则 ``count`` 和 ``top`` 结果将从这些"
"值中任意选择。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:81 of
msgid ""
"For mixed data types provided via a ``DataFrame``, the default is to "
"return only an analysis of numeric columns. If the dataframe consists "
"only of object data without any numeric columns, the default is to return"
" an analysis of object columns. If ``include='all'`` is provided as an "
"option, the result will include a union of attributes of each type."
msgstr ""
"对于通过 ``DataFrame`` 提供的混合数据类型，默认只返回数值列的分析结果。"
"如果 DataFrame 仅包含对象型数据而没有数值列，则默认返回对象列的分析结果。"
"如果提供了 ``include='all'`` 选项，则结果将包括每种数据类型的属性并集。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:87 of
msgid ""
"The `include` and `exclude` parameters can be used to limit which columns"
" in a ``DataFrame`` are analyzed for the output. The parameters are "
"ignored when analyzing a ``Series``."
msgstr ""
"`include` 和 `exclude` 参数可用于限制 ``DataFrame`` 中哪些列被分析以生成"
"输出。在分析 ``Series`` 时，这些参数将被忽略。"

