msgstr "通过属性访问方式描述 ``DataFrame`` 中的一列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:156 of
msgid "Including only numeric columns in a ``DataFrame`` description."
msgstr "在 ``DataFrame`` 描述中仅包含数值列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.describe.describe:169 of
msgid "Including only string columns in a ``DataFrame`` description."
msgstr "在 ``DataFrame`` 描述中仅包含字符串列。"

